Annerie Maria Magdalena Weber (amụrụ na 2 Julaị 1967) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa nke na-eje ozi dị ka onye otu National Assembly of South Africa
Onye otu Democratic Alliance, a họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ onye omeiwu na Mee 2019
Weber jere ozi dị ka onye isi oche nke DA's caucus na Nkangala District Municipality n'etiti afọ 2015 na 2019.

Weber nwetara BMus na BA Honours na Psychology na Mahadum North-West. O nwetara diplọma na mmekọrịta ụlọ ọrụ site na Vaal Triangle Campus nke mahadum. Site na Mahadum nke South Africa, o nwere diplọma agụmakwụkwọ dị elu
Weber nwetara asambodo nlekota na nyocha site na National School of Governance.

Weber jere ozi dị ka onye nduzi mpaghara nke Democratic Alliance na Mpumalanga site na 2012 ruo 2014. Site na 2015 ruo 2019, ọ bụ onye isi oche nke caucus nke pati ahụ na Nkangala District Municipality.
Na Machị 2018, a họpụtara ya dị ka onye isi oche mpaghara nke Democratic Alliance's Women Network.
Mgbe ntuli aka nke e mere na 8 Mee 2019, a họpụtara Weber ka ọ nọchite anya DA na ndị omeiwu. A ṅụrụ ya iyi dị ka onye otu National Assembly na 22 Mee 2019
Na 27 June 2019, ọ natara ọrụ kọmitii ya.
